title: Human Foals - Antidotes
description:
The Human Foals album 'Antidotes'.

The Human Foals are an electronic Foals cover band. This album contains all 11 electronic covers of Foals debut album Antidotes.

1. The French Open
2. Cassius
3. Red Socks Pugie
4. Olympic Airways
5. Electric Bloom
6. Balloons
7. Heavy Water
8. Two Steps Twice
9. Big Big Love (Fig. 2)
10. Like Swimming
11. Tron
